Output assets/feedforge-demo.gif

Require make

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set FontFamily "Menlo"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 380
Set Padding 24
Set Margin 12
Set MarginFill "#101820"
Set BorderRadius 8
Set WindowBar "Rings"
Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "export PS1='feedforge $ '; clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "make demo"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 7s
